Destroy Orc weapons and vile supplies in Banám Lugaun

The Orc encampment of Banám Lugaun watches Minas Morgul from across the Morgulduin River, and it harbours supplies and weapons for the Orcs. Destroying these weapons and ruining the supplies will surely throw some of the Orc plans into disarray and aid the work of Faramir and his Rangers in the Morgul Vale.
You destroyed many of the supplies and weapons that the Orcs rely upon, and by doing so you have secured safer passage for the Rangers scouting north of the river.
Destroyed many Orc weapons and vile supplies in Banám Lugaun.
An Orc camp sits between Minas Morgul and Cirith Ungol, and troops and supplies use it as they move through the treacherous terrain.
